<td data-valign="TOP" width="45%"><p>(4.833-841) <span id="4.833-841"></span> Thus she spake, and Thetis answered with these words: "If the fury of the ravening flame and the stormy winds cease in very deed, surely will I promise boldly to save the ship, even though the waves bar the way, if only the west wind blows fresh and clear. But it is time to fare on a long and measureless path, in quest of my sisters who will aid me, and to the spot where the ship's hawsers are fastened, that at early dawn the heroes may take thought to win their home-return."</p></td>
<td data-valign="TOP" width="10%"></td>
